<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3621] The timeout handler in AssignmentManager does an RPC while holding lock on RIT; a big no-no</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3621</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;J-D found this debugging a failure on Dmitriy&apos;s cluster; we&apos;re RPC&apos;ing under a synchronized(regionsInTransition).  Fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12501089">HBASE-3621</key>
            <summary>The timeout handler in AssignmentManager does an RPC while holding lock on RIT; a big no-no</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">Bug</type>
